{{Infobox museum | name = Esmeralda Municipal Museum | native_name = Museo Municipal de Esmeralda | native_name_lang = Spanish | image = | imagesize = | caption = | coordinates = | established = {{Start date|1982|12|30|df=y}} | location = [[Esmeralda, Cuba|Esmeralda]], [[Cuba]] | website = <!-- {{URL|example.com}} --> }} '''Esmeralda Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in Martí street in [[Esmeralda, Cuba|Esmeralda]], [[Cuba]]. It was established on 30 December 1982.<ref>[http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/565 Museo Municipal de Esmeralda]</ref>
