{{italic title}}
: ''For the Nynorsk dictionary with the same title, see [[Norsk Ordbok (Nynorsk)]]''

'''''Norsk ordbok''''' ('''''NO''''') is a [[dictionary]] of written Norwegian ([[Riksmål]] and moderate [[Bokmål]]). It was first published (by [[Kunnskapsforlaget]]) in 1993 under the title '''''Norsk illustrert ordbok'''''. Editor is [[Tor Guttu]].

Its full name is '''''Norsk ordbok; riksmål og moderat bokmål; med 1000 illustrasjoner'''''.

A digital edition is available at [[Ordnett.no]]. 

==External links==
* [http://www.ordnett.no/ Ordnett] – Norwegian pay site with several dictionaries.

